{"tid":1241730,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"AKB48本家討論區#41 垃圾48等天收 營運老母問候區","createTime":"2019-06-18T21:37:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T13:04:31.000Z","uid":35137,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e85c129b5e921acf6e09764def5be58c985f627d","tid":1241730,"uid":35137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T21:37:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jjC0hT7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjjC0hT7.jpg&h=32e97d94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">初心？初你老母！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔知有無人睇既前言:<br />\n<br />\n雖然最近推得唔快,但本區宗旨係悠閒既聚腳點,唔求幾十日爆po,但求大家得閒貼下圖吹兩句就好,歡迎各路人馬加入本家大家庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n蒙大家錯愛,本PO可以開到40,想再次重申開番本家PO既原意係希望俾各位本家飯有個集中地吹奏自己個推,無論貼圖又好、放mb活動既情報上黎又好、打機過唔到、番工辛苦吐苦水,甚至想講自己同MB已經有默契,心入面有各自既位置都無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n明白到現今世代好多48飯都係各團互走,亦唔介意大家偶爾貼下其他分團既成員介紹俾其他會員知道,總之唔好貼到或宣傳到呢度變左100%既分團討論區就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實呢邊規矩好簡單:<br />\n1. 唔明或有野想知可以問其他巴打或google。<br />\n2. 討論過程實有爭論或嘈交,基本上唔好人身攻擊就得。<br />\n3. 明白到理論上<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">除左完美既奈奈</span></span>無一個MB係完美既,黑還黑、恥笑還恥笑,唔好太過分傷到成員既飯既感情就好了。<br />\n4. 8仔算唔算本家?有人算有人唔算,呢邊無咩所謂都歡迎討論同吹奏。<br />\n5.本PO歡迎mb生日圖海洗1001,唔好分開2日洗就ok。<br />\n6.萬一真係咁唔好彩有會員唔小心自爆左,麻煩大家唔好引用落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n7.如果係吹奏46團或想撩人過檔請麻煩番去46團既相關po,有緣既話巴打們自然會過去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n8.通常啲會員今日叫緊某mb做老婆然後下個月同你講其實仲有其他老婆,係伏筆黎<br />\n9.本家PO飯聚主要話題：今個月買左幾多對鞋同件褸,我=毒撚專心食飯答唔到嘴<br />\n10.世界仔剩係反牙達<br />\n11.本區識日文班人睇5ch攞料,唔識個班就睇百度/貓頭<br />\n12. 本家區三大黨派:自稱本家死忠既船團&amp;柏木黨&amp;萌夏黨<br />\n13.MARY:好想一生一世守護__ __BB豬(每星期更新)<br />\n14.唔好諗咁多,本家全純血出既單曲應該唔會有機會出到<br />\n15.本家最新最後最強希望就係矢作萌夏<br />\n<del>16.NGT連贊助商都同佢哋割席就知佢哋好快會執</del><br />\n17.<del>已經消失的10專和56單</del><br />\n18.以為睇垃圾泡狗就好似高人一等咁,得喇得喇,知啦知啦,叻啦叻啦,死開啲啦<br />\n19.目前有預定既活動得番8月握手會<br />\n一切既知識:<br />\n<a href=\"http://google.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoogle.com&d=HhKtR2wUfRZLc9nBt5dK8AOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=7989210f\" target=\"_blank\">http://google.com</a><br />\n<br />\n特別鳴謝會然I am Mary：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1qFHsr_JzhWwiRAkGOCu0185Od67ERVVM63E1bj309o4/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1qFHsr_JzhWwiRAkGOCu0185Od67ERVVM63E1bj309o4%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=HhKtR2wUfRZLc9nBt5dK8AOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=24c1b25c\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1qFHsr_JzhWwiRAkGOCu0185Od67ERVVM63E1bj309o4/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n握手流程攻略 KEEP住UPDATE<br />\n<br />\n其他諗到再加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote]"},{"pid":"23d5f9c8a4fbeadee4bd594506ca8721b1803af6","tid":1241730,"uid":11880,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T23:56:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/0aa/f1d/0aaf1d954ced72c31639a410f1f488761a2efdbd_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2F0aa%2Ff1d%2F0aaf1d954ced72c31639a410f1f488761a2efdbd_n.jpg&h=76161ded&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"179ab6933f6999f338723b2a597987302011fdfa","tid":1241730,"uid":5831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T23:59:21.000Z","msg":"大佬樓主開過咁既topic 咩玩法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edfea869986724dca0bf143a88de16f151c68d2b","tid":1241730,"uid":239855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:05:25.000Z","msg":"樓主做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e0cfc3889de013dd614db4e87a6994394ecd0bb","tid":1241730,"uid":43543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0